modShortDescription: We love getting station schematic but 5 on day 3 takes the fun out of it. This 7 Days to Die mod makes schematics looted from destroyed stations more rare.
modDescription:
We all love getting a station schematic but 5 on day 3 takes the fun out of it. This 7 Days to Die mod makes schematics [loot](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-loot/)ed from destroyed stations more rare.

[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/JaxTeller718/JaxTeller718_Modlets_Stable/tree/master/JaxTeller718_ReducedStationSchematics)

If you appreciate JaxTeller718’s work here feel free to use this [donate link](https://www.paypal.me/FrankCirabisiJr) to show support.

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/8098-jaxteller718-modlet-collection/).

**Credits:** [JaxTeller718](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/jaxteller718/)
